{"storyMeta":{"storyReviewType":"NONE","storyId":"act25side_level_act25side_08_end","storyGroup":"act25side","storySort":18,"storyDependence":"act25side_level_act25side_08_beg","storyCanShow":1,"storyCode":"CW-8","storyName":"过去与现在的交会","storyPic":null,"storyInfo":"雅拉阻止赫默，凯尔希阻止“保存者”。一道光柱在特里蒙城中升起。","storyCanEnter":1,"storyTxt":"activities/act25side/level_act25side_08_end","avgTag":"行动后","unLockType":"STAGE_CLEAR","costItemType":"NONE","costItemId":null,"costItemCount":0,"stageCount":1,"requiredStages":[{"stageId":"act25side_08","minState":"PASS","maxState":"COMPLETE"}],"prev":16,"next":18,"characters":["？？？","凯尔希","赫默","雅拉","“保存者”","娜斯提","小贾斯汀"]},"lines":[{"type":"HEADER","key":"title_test","skippable":"true","mode":"BLACK_MASK","text":"","id":0},{"type":"stopmusic","id":1},{"type":"dialog","id":2},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":3},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":4},{"type":"Background","image":"38_g8_storage","screenadapt":"coverall","id":5},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":6},{"type":"playMusic","intro":"$act17_intro","key":"$act17_loop","volume":"0.6","id":7,"musicid":0},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":8},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":9},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_avg_energybody","volume":"1","id":10},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":11},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"我命令你回答我，仆从。","id":12},{"type":"dialog","id":13},{"type":"Decision","options":[{"id":"15","text":"仆、仆从......？"},{"id":"15","text":"......"},{"id":"15","text":"我可不是凯尔希的仆从......"}],"values":[],"id":14},{"type":"Predicate","references":["1","2","3"],"id":15,"end":32},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"char_003_kalts_1#1","duration":"1","isblock":"true","id":16},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"......Dr.{@nickname}失去了记忆。博士并不是你认识的那些人中的任何一个，不再是了。","id":17,"figure":"char_003_kalts_1#1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"博士现在是泰拉的一员，罗德岛的一员。","id":18,"figure":"char_003_kalts_1#1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"我们已经共同经历了许多，直至今日。","id":19,"figure":"char_003_kalts_1#1"},{"type":"charslot","id":20},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"......罗德岛？","id":21},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"（未知语言）罗德岛？","id":22},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"......原来如此。","id":23},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"所以，“失忆”。为什么你不把所有事情重新告诉这个......“博士”？","id":24},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"char_003_kalts_1#1","id":25},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"......","id":26,"figure":"char_003_kalts_1#1"},{"type":"charslot","id":27},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"啊，我知道了。","id":28},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"你始终在怀疑这个“博士”的真实性。比起复原一段不再可信的记忆，你更相信一个重新认识世界的他。","id":29},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"嗯......也不奇怪。地面上发生的一切都做不得假，如果真的有足够的干预，泰拉不该是如今的形态。","id":30},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"看来并没有任何事情如我们所愿。尽管你不记得了......Dr.{@nickname}。","id":31},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"这是多么难得的机会。在这里，遇见你们。却是这样的情况......","id":32,"end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":33},{"type":"Decision","options":[{"id":"35","text":"......"}],"values":[],"id":34},{"type":"Predicate","references":["1"],"id":35,"end":37},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"那么，失忆的“Dr.{@nickname}”与自称凯尔希的AMa-10，你们来这里又是为了什么？","id":36},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"克丽斯腾让你们感到紧张吗？这一切超出了你们的控制吗？","id":37,"end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":38},{"type":"Decision","options":[{"id":"40","text":"你好像还没有回答我的问题。"},{"id":"40","text":"别这么高高在上！"},{"id":"40","text":"自我介绍是平等交谈的开始。"}],"values":[],"id":39},{"type":"Predicate","references":["1","2","3"],"id":40,"end":45},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"......","id":41},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"我是计划的人格模拟，数万年来始终守望着这座黑暗的大厅，还有数十万同胞冰冷的身体。","id":42},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"我曾是最后的希望，一次悲观的尝试，一个虚无主义的代名词。","id":43},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"但现在，或许对渺小的你们而言......我是克丽斯腾疯狂计划的帮凶和幕后黑手。","id":44},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"我是行将就木的“保存者”，敬畏你眼里的所有，我是文明的消亡本身。","id":45,"end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":46},{"type":"musicvolume","volume":"0.2","fadetime":"2","id":47},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":48},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":49},{"type":"Background","image":"38_g15_energywell_glowed","screenadapt":"coverall","id":50},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":51},{"type":"musicvolume","volume":"0.6","fadetime":"2","id":52},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":53},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":54},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"1","id":55},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_1031_slent2_1#1$2","duration":"1.5","isblock":"true","id":56},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"位置没错，递质的反应......很强烈......","id":57,"figure":"avg_1031_slent2_1#1$2"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_1031_slent2_1#4$2","id":58},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"我——","id":59,"figure":"avg_1031_slent2_1#4$2"},{"type":"dialog","id":60},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","posfrom":"0,0","posto":"0,-80","duration":"0.5","id":61},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_893_1#9$1","posfrom":"-300,0","posto":"0,-50","duration":"0.5","isblock":"true","id":62},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$bodyfalldown3","volume":"1","id":63},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":64},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","posfrom":"0,-80","posto":"0,0","duration":"1.5","id":65},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","posfrom":"0,-50","posto":"0,0","duration":"1.5","isblock":"true","id":66},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","posfrom":"0,0","posto":"250,0","duration":"2","isblock":"true","id":67},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":68},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_1031_slent2_1#9$2","focus":"m","id":69},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"雅拉主任......？","id":70,"figure":"avg_1031_slent2_1#9$2"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"您怎么在这里？","id":71,"figure":"avg_1031_slent2_1#9$2"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_893_1#9$1","focus":"l","id":72},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"雅拉","text":"你带着我的祝福，走到了这里，也好。","id":73,"figure":"avg_npc_893_1#9$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_1031_slent2_1#1$2","focus":"m","id":74},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"......","id":75,"figure":"avg_1031_slent2_1#1$2"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_1031_slent2_1#5$2","focus":"m","id":76},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"您......是为了阻止我而来的。","id":77,"figure":"avg_1031_slent2_1#5$2"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_893_1#10$1","focus":"l","id":78},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"雅拉","text":"你没有松开我送你的武器，我很高兴。","id":79,"figure":"avg_npc_893_1#10$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"雅拉","text":"看起来你也并不是因为一腔热血才站在这里的。","id":80,"figure":"avg_npc_893_1#10$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_1031_slent2_1#5$2","focus":"m","id":81},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"是的。","id":82,"figure":"avg_1031_slent2_1#5$2"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_893_1#9$1","focus":"l","id":83},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"雅拉","text":"这是你最后的机会了，孩子。","id":84,"figure":"avg_npc_893_1#9$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"雅拉","text":"抽身而出，还是继续？","id":85,"figure":"avg_npc_893_1#9$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_1031_slent2_1#5$2","focus":"m","id":86},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"我会......学着成为您所说的战士的，雅拉主任。","id":87,"figure":"avg_1031_slent2_1#5$2"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_893_1#9$1","focus":"l","id":88},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"雅拉","text":"......","id":89,"figure":"avg_npc_893_1#9$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"雅拉","text":"赫默，你很清楚，克丽斯腾不会把聚焦发生器接收的能量对准大地上任何一处城镇。","id":90,"figure":"avg_npc_893_1#9$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"雅拉","text":"你没有必要阻止她。","id":91,"figure":"avg_npc_893_1#9$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"雅拉","text":"她只是和所有科学家一样，准备向无人曾踏足的地方前进罢了。","id":92,"figure":"avg_npc_893_1#9$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_1031_slent2_1#1$2","focus":"m","id":93},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"也许吧，雅拉主任。","id":94,"figure":"avg_1031_slent2_1#1$2"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_1031_slent2_1#2$2","focus":"m","id":95},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"我并不如您一样了解总辖，但如果是您说的话，我愿意相信。","id":96,"figure":"avg_1031_slent2_1#2$2"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_1031_slent2_1#1$2","focus":"m","id":97},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"但我会继续试着停下这一切，就算是您挡在我面前也不例外。","id":98,"figure":"avg_1031_slent2_1#1$2"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_893_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":99},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"雅拉","text":"......为什么？","id":100,"figure":"avg_npc_893_1#1$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_1031_slent2_1#1$2","focus":"m","id":101},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"因为，如果总辖就这么进行了她无论是什么的实验，并且获得了成功——","id":102,"figure":"avg_1031_slent2_1#1$2"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"我们都知道，她可是莱茵生命的总辖，无论是出于情感上的信任还是理性的判断，她都很有可能成功。","id":103,"figure":"avg_1031_slent2_1#1$2"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_1031_slent2_1#5$2","focus":"m","id":104},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"您认为，哥伦比亚的研究者们会怎么看待她？","id":105,"figure":"avg_1031_slent2_1#5$2"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"您在莱茵生命的人力资源考察科工作了这么久，这里的人您再了解不过。","id":106,"figure":"avg_1031_slent2_1#5$2"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_893_1#8$1","focus":"l","id":107},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"雅拉","text":"......英雄。","id":108,"figure":"avg_npc_893_1#8$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"雅拉","text":"克丽斯腾会成为哥伦比亚科学界的英雄和偶像。","id":109,"figure":"avg_npc_893_1#8$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_1031_slent2_1#1$2","focus":"m","id":110},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"是啊，她会成为科学家的榜样，成为研究者的标杆。","id":111,"figure":"avg_1031_slent2_1#1$2"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_1031_slent2_1#5$2","focus":"m","id":112},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"......然后，这样的事就再也不会停止。","id":113,"figure":"avg_1031_slent2_1#5$2"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"一桩一桩，一件一件，研究者们乐此不疲。","id":114,"figure":"avg_1031_slent2_1#5$2"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"但是，雅拉主任，只有她是克丽斯腾·莱特，只有她。","id":115,"figure":"avg_1031_slent2_1#5$2"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_1031_slent2_1#10$2","focus":"m","id":116},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"其他的那些自诩引领者与天才的人呢？其他的那些被这种所谓的“不择手段的拓荒精神”鼓舞的人呢？","id":117,"figure":"avg_1031_slent2_1#10$2"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"其他那些将自己的偏执或理想付诸实践，无所顾忌的人呢？","id":118,"figure":"avg_1031_slent2_1#10$2"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"那些贪婪的，狂妄的，冒进的，顽固的，与我们一样的人呢？","id":119,"figure":"avg_1031_slent2_1#10$2"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"如果他们都把如同莱茵生命的总辖一般行事作为美德——","id":120,"figure":"avg_1031_slent2_1#10$2"},{"type":"dialog","id":121},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":122},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_1031_slent2_1#5$2","focus":"m","id":123},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"如果是您，一定能想象到，那是怎样一种未来。","id":124,"figure":"avg_1031_slent2_1#5$2"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_1031_slent2_1#4$2","focus":"m","id":125},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"或许我们都不用想象......","id":126,"figure":"avg_1031_slent2_1#4$2"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"您对莱茵生命已经做过的那些研究，也从来不是一无所知。","id":127,"figure":"avg_1031_slent2_1#4$2"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_893_1#9$1","focus":"l","id":128},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"雅拉","text":"我很清楚，赫默。","id":129,"figure":"avg_npc_893_1#9$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"雅拉","text":"我很清楚，特里蒙，不，哥伦比亚的国土内，曾发生过，且正发生着多少这样的事情。","id":130,"figure":"avg_npc_893_1#9$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"雅拉","text":"曾有无数疯狂而诱人的计划摆在我的面前，拿出这些东西的人眼神明亮，笑容真诚。","id":131,"figure":"avg_npc_893_1#9$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"雅拉","text":"他们衷心地以为他们在为“纯粹的科学”效力，是我们认知原野的拓荒者。","id":132,"figure":"avg_npc_893_1#9$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_1031_slent2_1#5$2","focus":"m","id":133},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"而您和您的同僚们，只需要评估他们的实验计划里，宏伟蓝图下，会不会偶尔也要付出一点点“代价”和“损耗”。","id":134,"figure":"avg_1031_slent2_1#5$2"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_893_1#9$1","focus":"l","id":135},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"雅拉","text":"“代价”。","id":136,"figure":"avg_npc_893_1#9$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"雅拉","text":"这种代价有时是一片肥沃的土地，有时是若干个绝症病人或者死刑犯；有时是一个村落或一个城镇，有时是某个特定的种族乃至国家。","id":137,"figure":"avg_npc_893_1#9$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_893_1#6$1","focus":"l","id":138},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"雅拉","text":"在我看来，也有时，是他们自己。","id":139,"figure":"avg_npc_893_1#6$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_1031_slent2_1#5$2","focus":"m","id":140},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"您对此恐惧吗，雅拉主任？还是，您也为了科学进步的可能性而兴奋不已？","id":141,"figure":"avg_1031_slent2_1#5$2"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_1031_slent2_1#10$2","focus":"m","id":142},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"雅拉主任，这世上从来没有装在玻璃罩里的“纯粹的科学”。","id":143,"figure":"avg_1031_slent2_1#10$2"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"科学在我们的手掌中，在人的手掌中。您必须知道它的温度，它的重量，它是否灼人，它会带来什么痛苦或是慰藉。","id":144,"figure":"avg_1031_slent2_1#10$2"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"那些人永远声称自己是在前进，可他们只是胡乱把脚伸向自己想践踏的地方而已。","id":145,"figure":"avg_1031_slent2_1#10$2"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_893_1#8$1","focus":"l","id":146},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"雅拉","text":"但，赫默，这就是前进。","id":147,"figure":"avg_npc_893_1#8$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"雅拉","text":"没有人知道路在哪，他们只能这么走。","id":148,"figure":"avg_npc_893_1#8$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"雅拉","text":"幸运者找对了地方，走入光明中。不幸者闯进死胡同，兜兜转转。","id":149,"figure":"avg_npc_893_1#8$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_893_1#9$1","focus":"l","id":150},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"雅拉","text":"但你没办法让他们停下的。","id":151,"figure":"avg_npc_893_1#9$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"雅拉","text":"你自己也是研究者，你知道什么最无法阻挡。","id":152,"figure":"avg_npc_893_1#9$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_1031_slent2_1#5$2","focus":"m","id":153},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"......","id":154,"figure":"avg_1031_slent2_1#5$2"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_893_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":155},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"雅拉","text":"——是渴求。","id":156,"figure":"avg_npc_893_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"雅拉","text":"物质束缚不了它，道德束缚不了它，规则也同样束缚不了它。","id":157,"figure":"avg_npc_893_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"雅拉","text":"这片大地上，从古至今，在克丽斯腾之前，你说的那些贪婪的、狂妄的、冒进的、顽固的人们，他们又何曾停下过？","id":158,"figure":"avg_npc_893_1#1$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_1031_slent2_1#5$2","focus":"m","id":159},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"那么，今后，他们必须停下。","id":160,"figure":"avg_1031_slent2_1#5$2"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"起码，在真正俯身看清自己的脚下到底是什么之前，他们必须停下。","id":161,"figure":"avg_1031_slent2_1#5$2"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_1031_slent2_1#2$2","focus":"m","id":162},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"雅拉主任，我觉得——科学的燃料不该是欲望与理想，也不该是计算与取舍。","id":163,"figure":"avg_1031_slent2_1#2$2"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_1031_slent2_1#1$2","focus":"m","id":164},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"科学是真切地看向每一个人。","id":165,"figure":"avg_1031_slent2_1#1$2"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_893_1#2$1","focus":"l","id":166},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"雅拉","text":"......","id":167,"figure":"avg_npc_893_1#2$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_893_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":168},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"雅拉","text":"赫默，你说了一句很漂亮的话，适合被挂在大学图书馆的走廊里。","id":169,"figure":"avg_npc_893_1#1$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_893_1#9$1","focus":"l","id":170},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"雅拉","text":"但恐怕没有哪个研究者愿意让这句话出现在实验室的墙上。","id":171,"figure":"avg_npc_893_1#9$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"雅拉","text":"这是句空话。","id":172,"figure":"avg_npc_893_1#9$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_1031_slent2_1#5$2","focus":"m","id":173},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"那么，我会让它落实的，雅拉主任。","id":174,"figure":"avg_1031_slent2_1#5$2"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_1031_slent2_1#1$2","focus":"m","id":175},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"我不想中途放弃，我还带着您的祝福。","id":176,"figure":"avg_1031_slent2_1#1$2"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_893_1#8$1","focus":"l","id":177},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"雅拉","text":"......","id":178,"figure":"avg_npc_893_1#8$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_893_1#9$1","focus":"l","id":179},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"雅拉","text":"赫默，克丽斯腾花了很长时间准备这项计划，我不知道她为此付出了多少。","id":180,"figure":"avg_npc_893_1#9$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"雅拉","text":"但她的觉悟一定不会比她的父母要少。","id":181,"figure":"avg_npc_893_1#9$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_893_1#11$1","focus":"l","id":182},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"雅拉","text":"你——","id":183,"figure":"avg_npc_893_1#11$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_893_1#6$1","focus":"l","id":184},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"雅拉","text":"好吧......不是你，是我。","id":185,"figure":"avg_npc_893_1#6$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"雅拉","text":"......我无法眼睁睁地看着，希望又一次沦为泡影。","id":186,"figure":"avg_npc_893_1#6$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_1031_slent2_1#1$2","focus":"m","id":187},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"那么，雅拉主任，您希望的又是什么？见证克丽斯腾的成功，还是让她平安无事地回来？","id":188,"figure":"avg_1031_slent2_1#1$2"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_893_1#6$1","focus":"l","id":189},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"雅拉","text":"......","id":190,"figure":"avg_npc_893_1#6$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_1031_slent2_1#1$2","focus":"m","id":191},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"我认识位叫露比的研究员，她最大的希望是按时下班，顺利退休。","id":192,"figure":"avg_1031_slent2_1#1$2"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"刚才遇到的一位士兵先生，我想他现在唯一希望的事就是从这座失控的能量井平安离开，带着亲戚们从特里蒙的科学疯子手中逃走。","id":193,"figure":"avg_1031_slent2_1#1$2"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_1031_slent2_1#1$2","focus":"m","id":194},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"与他们相比，总辖的希望更高贵吗？","id":195,"figure":"avg_1031_slent2_1#1$2"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"因为她想要的东西，足够“进步”？","id":196,"figure":"avg_1031_slent2_1#1$2"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_1031_slent2_1#2$2","focus":"m","id":197},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"还是只是因为，您与她之间的感情，足够紧密？","id":198,"figure":"avg_1031_slent2_1#2$2"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"雅拉主任，您知道这并不公平。","id":199,"figure":"avg_1031_slent2_1#2$2"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_1031_slent2_1#1$2","focus":"m","id":200},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"您不能这么自私。","id":201,"figure":"avg_1031_slent2_1#1$2"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_893_1#6$1","focus":"l","id":202},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"雅拉","text":"我......","id":203,"figure":"avg_npc_893_1#6$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"雅拉","text":"......","id":204,"figure":"avg_npc_893_1#6$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_893_1#9$1","focus":"l","id":205},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"雅拉","text":"我......就是这么自私，我没办法用道德或正义欺骗自己，然后放你过去。","id":206,"figure":"avg_npc_893_1#9$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_893_1#7$1","focus":"l","id":207},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"雅拉","text":"我们必须承认感情的重量，克丽斯腾的那个梦，我没办法袖手旁观。","id":208,"figure":"avg_npc_893_1#7$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"雅拉","text":"......赫默，你不会不明白。","id":209,"figure":"avg_npc_893_1#7$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_1031_slent2_1#10$2","focus":"m","id":210},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"可如果我们能阻止总辖，她也许还会——","id":211,"figure":"avg_1031_slent2_1#10$2"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_893_1#6$1","focus":"l","id":212},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"雅拉","text":"不会的。","id":213,"figure":"avg_npc_893_1#6$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"雅拉","text":"不会的，孩子。","id":214,"figure":"avg_npc_893_1#6$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"雅拉","text":"我很清楚......当她开始这项计划的时候，就没有打算再回来了。","id":215,"figure":"avg_npc_893_1#6$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"雅拉","text":"从很早之前，甚至，在我们初见时，这一切......就已经无法挽回了。","id":216,"figure":"avg_npc_893_1#6$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_893_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":217},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"雅拉","text":"赫默，对于你能挡在我的面前，我很欣慰。我甚至可以说，我支持你的主张。","id":218,"figure":"avg_npc_893_1#1$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_893_1#6$1","focus":"l","id":219},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"雅拉","text":"但是，作为克丽斯腾的......","id":220,"figure":"avg_npc_893_1#6$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"雅拉","text":"......","id":221,"figure":"avg_npc_893_1#6$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_893_1#9$1","focus":"l","id":222},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"雅拉","text":"......家人，我依然不会让你通过。","id":223,"figure":"avg_npc_893_1#9$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_893_1#7$1","focus":"l","id":224},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"雅拉","text":"就让我看看吧，你真的......准备好承担你所说的话了吗？","id":225,"figure":"avg_npc_893_1#7$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"雅拉","text":"你今后将要面对的，不再是一个帕尔维斯或者克丽斯腾。","id":226,"figure":"avg_npc_893_1#7$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"雅拉","text":"你要面对的，是所有试图前进的人们。","id":227,"figure":"avg_npc_893_1#7$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_1031_slent2_1#2$2","focus":"m","id":228},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"......","id":229,"figure":"avg_1031_slent2_1#2$2"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_1031_slent2_1#1$2","focus":"m","id":230},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"我会的，我必须准备好，我向您保证。","id":231,"figure":"avg_1031_slent2_1#1$2"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"科学必须前进，也势必前进。","id":232,"figure":"avg_1031_slent2_1#1$2"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"也许，有的人，比如总辖，他们更擅长“前进”的部分。","id":233,"figure":"avg_1031_slent2_1#1$2"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_1031_slent2_1#5$2","focus":"m","id":234},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"但也必须有人站出来，确保科学——","id":235,"figure":"avg_1031_slent2_1#5$2"},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_avg_drone","volume":"1","id":236},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"依然在人的手中。","id":237,"figure":"avg_1031_slent2_1#5$2"},{"type":"dialog","id":238},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","posfrom":"250,0","posto":"50,0","duration":"0.3","id":239},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_avg_clothmovement","volume":"1","id":240},{"type":"delay","time":"0.2","id":241},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$swordtsing4","volume":"1","id":242},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","action":"shake","power":"5","times":"60","duration":"0.5","id":243},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":244},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":245},{"type":"charslot","id":246},{"type":"Background","image":"38_g8_storage","screenadapt":"coverall","id":247},{"type":"delay","time":"3","id":248},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"char_003_kalts_1#3","id":249},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":250},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"char_003_kalts_1#3","id":251},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"......“保存者”......","id":252,"figure":"char_003_kalts_1#3"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"我没有想到，居然真的是您。","id":253,"figure":"char_003_kalts_1#3"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"可如果是您，又怎么会......","id":254,"figure":"char_003_kalts_1#3"},{"type":"charslot","id":255},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“保存者”","text":"协助一只小动物的疯狂计划？","id":256},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“保存者”","text":"还是目睹一个年幼文明踏出摇篮的第一步？","id":257},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“保存者”","text":"你来得太晚了，“博士”。","id":258},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“保存者”","text":"我的等待......已经失去了意义。","id":259},{"type":"dialog","id":260},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","focus":"none","id":261},{"type":"Decision","options":[{"id":"263","text":"和眼前的事比起来，特里蒙发生的一切都好像不值一提。"},{"id":"263","text":"......"},{"id":"263","text":"......我需要更多解释。"}],"values":[],"id":262},{"type":"Predicate","references":["1","2","3"],"id":263,"end":284},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"char_003_kalts_1#3","id":264},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"是您在帮助克丽斯腾。她以某种手段与您有所接触。","id":265,"figure":"char_003_kalts_1#3"},{"type":"charslot","id":266},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“保存者”","text":"泰拉的历史、文化、语言、种族、科技水平，通过哥伦比亚的网络，我已尽数知晓。","id":267},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“保存者”","text":"可笑的是，如今地面上的信息传输甚至无法做到覆盖全球，而你们相互毁灭的手段，倒是有了合格的演化效率。","id":268},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"char_003_kalts_1#1","id":269},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"泰拉的手段过于原始且依赖源石，以这样的转换率，想实现克丽斯腾的尝试......需要的能源也是匪夷所思的。","id":270,"figure":"char_003_kalts_1#1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"char_003_kalts_1#3","id":271},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"泰拉几乎不可能有技术手段解决这一难题。除非——","id":272,"figure":"char_003_kalts_1#3"},{"type":"charslot","id":273},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“保存者”","text":"是的。","id":274},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“保存者”","text":"我把最后的血给了她，供养一颗新的心脏，也许好过守着一盏将熄的灯。","id":275},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"char_003_kalts_1#3","id":276},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"......","id":277,"figure":"char_003_kalts_1#3"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"您竟然，真的——","id":278,"figure":"char_003_kalts_1#3"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"......为什么不惜如此？这是您在这么漫长的时间里的所有努力......全都白费了。","id":279,"figure":"char_003_kalts_1#3"},{"type":"charslot","id":280},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“保存者”","text":"是啊，白费了。","id":281},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“保存者”","text":"计划被我亲自关闭，指令由我亲自输入。","id":282},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“保存者”","text":"这是我不容懊悔的判断。","id":283},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“保存者”","text":"很快了，很快。","id":284,"end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":285},{"type":"charslot","id":286},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"5","xstrength":"30","ystrength":"30","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":287},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_avg_collapse","volume":"1","id":288},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":289},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0.4","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.1","block":"true","id":290},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":291},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":292},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0.5","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.1","block":"true","id":293},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":294},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0.9","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.3","block":"true","id":295},{"type":"delay","time":"0.6","id":296},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":297},{"type":"Text","text":"巨大的震动从远处蔓延而来，地下空间的灯光闪烁了几下。","id":298},{"type":"Text","text":"那位自称“保存者”的存在沉默了片刻，又好像是深深叹了一口气。","id":299},{"type":"dialog","id":300},{"type":"Decision","options":[{"id":"302","text":"怎、怎么了？！"},{"id":"302","text":"......"},{"id":"302","text":"难道是能量井？"}],"values":[],"id":301},{"type":"Predicate","references":["1","2","3"],"id":302,"end":304},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“保存者”","text":"这只是婴儿好奇的一瞥——","id":303},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“保存者”","text":"却要跨越什么样的阻碍？","id":304,"end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":305},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":306},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":307},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1","id":308},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":309},{"type":"Text","text":"8:11 P.M. 能量井异常蓄能","id":310},{"type":"dialog","id":311},{"type":"Background","image":"38_g15_energywell_glowed","screenadapt":"coverall","id":312},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":313},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_avg_magic_3","volume":"1","id":314},{"type":"delay","time":"0.8","id":315},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$swordtsing5","volume":"1","id":316},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":317},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_avg_ftrub","volume":"1","id":318},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_1031_slent2_1#9$2","posfrom":"-600,0","posto":"40,-20","duration":"1","isblock":"true","id":319},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":320},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","posfrom":"40,-20","posto":"0,0","duration":"1.5","isblock":"true","id":321},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"1","id":322},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_893_1#1$1","posfrom":"-300,0","posto":"0,0","duration":"2.5","isblock":"true","id":323},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":324},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_893_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":325},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"雅拉","text":"那家叫罗德岛的企业给了你很好的训练。","id":326,"figure":"avg_npc_893_1#1$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_1031_slent2_1#9$2","focus":"r","id":327},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"呼......呼......","id":328,"figure":"avg_1031_slent2_1#9$2"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_893_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":329},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"雅拉","text":"胳膊还能抬得起来吗？","id":330,"figure":"avg_npc_893_1#1$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_1031_slent2_1#1$2","focus":"r","id":331},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"我没事。","id":332,"figure":"avg_1031_slent2_1#1$2"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"您的胳膊呢？","id":333,"figure":"avg_1031_slent2_1#1$2"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_893_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":334},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"雅拉","text":"放心，我买了医疗保险。","id":335,"figure":"avg_npc_893_1#1$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_893_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":336},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"雅拉","text":"还要继续吗？","id":337,"figure":"avg_npc_893_1#1$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_1031_slent2_1#5$2","focus":"r","id":338},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"......如果您依然挡在我的面前的话。","id":339,"figure":"avg_1031_slent2_1#5$2"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_893_1#9$1","focus":"l","id":340},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"雅拉","text":"好吧，那就继续。","id":341,"figure":"avg_npc_893_1#9$1"},{"type":"dialog","id":342},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_avg_energywell","volume":"0","loop":"true","channel":"a","id":343},{"type":"SoundVolume","volume":"0.4","channel":"a","fadetime":"2","id":344},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":345},{"type":"playMusic","intro":"$act25side_intro","key":"$act25side_loop","volume":"0.6","id":346,"musicid":1},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_893_1#7$1","focus":"l","id":347},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"雅拉","text":"......等等，情况有些不对。","id":348,"figure":"avg_npc_893_1#7$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"雅拉","text":"这里的温度......就算是能量井准备发射，这里也不至于升到这种温度。","id":349,"figure":"avg_npc_893_1#7$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_1031_slent2_1#1$2","focus":"r","id":350},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"军方为了停止蓄能，几乎把这里所有的能源都切断了。","id":351,"figure":"avg_1031_slent2_1#1$2"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_893_1#3$1","focus":"l","id":352},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"雅拉","text":"包括所有的安全警报和控制系统？那帮蠢货——","id":353,"figure":"avg_npc_893_1#3$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"雅拉","text":"快！我们必须离开这里！","id":354,"figure":"avg_npc_893_1#3$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_1031_slent2_1#5$2","focus":"r","id":355},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"上面还有一些驻扎的士兵，雅拉主任，拜托您带他们离开。","id":356,"figure":"avg_1031_slent2_1#5$2"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_893_1#4$1","focus":"l","id":357},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"雅拉","text":"你要去哪？","id":358,"figure":"avg_npc_893_1#4$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_1031_slent2_1#1$2","focus":"r","id":359},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"控制系统的能源被切断了，为什么总辖还能实现对这里的远程操作？","id":360,"figure":"avg_1031_slent2_1#1$2"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_1031_slent2_1#5$2","focus":"r","id":361},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"递质的反应还在增强，我......还有机会。","id":362,"figure":"avg_1031_slent2_1#5$2"},{"type":"dialog","id":363},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$rungeneral","volume":"1","id":364},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","afrom":"1","ato":"0","duration":"1","focus":"r","isblock":"true","id":365},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":366},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","focus":"l","id":367},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"雅拉","text":"赫默！","id":368,"figure":"avg_npc_893_1#4$1"},{"type":"dialog","id":369},{"type":"charslot","duration":"0.5","id":370},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":371},{"type":"Image","image":"38_i15_1","screenadapt":"coverall","fadetime":"2","id":372},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"-1","xstrength":"10","ystrength":"10","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"false","block":"false","id":373},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_avg_collapse","volume":"1","id":374},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_avg_energywell","volume":"0.8","loop":"true","channel":"a","id":375},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":376},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":377},{"type":"Text","text":"热浪炙烤着雅拉的脸，那个她从前并未那么在意的黎博利研究员，正继续向能量井的更深层跑去。","id":378},{"type":"Text","text":"雅拉突然觉得，什么东西都无法成为那个身影的阻碍。","id":379},{"type":"Text","text":"也许，她答应过自己的事，真的会做到。","id":380},{"type":"Text","text":"她想，到了那时候，自己或许能帮上一点忙。","id":381},{"type":"dialog","id":382},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_avg_energywell","volume":"1","loop":"true","channel":"a","id":383},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"-1","xstrength":"15","ystrength":"15","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"false","block":"false","id":384},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_avg_collapse","volume":"1","id":385},{"type":"Image","image":"38_i15_2","screenadapt":"coverall","fadetime":"1","id":386},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":387},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":388},{"type":"delay","time":"3.5","id":389},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"雅拉","text":"看来发射的准备工作已经结束了。","id":390},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"雅拉","text":"“科学是真切地看向每一个人。”","id":391},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"雅拉","text":"哈，我可不是科学家。","id":392},{"type":"dialog","id":393},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_avg_energygather","volume":"1","id":394},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":395},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"雅拉","text":"克丽斯腾，你会飞上你所梦想的深空之中......","id":396},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"雅拉","text":"你一定会的。","id":397},{"type":"dialog","id":398},{"type":"StopSound","channel":"a","fadetime":"2","id":399},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":400},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":401},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.1","xstrength":"0","ystrength":"0","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"false","block":"false","id":402},{"type":"image","id":403},{"type":"charslot","id":404},{"type":"Background","image":"29_g7_mainstreet_n","screenadapt":"coverall","id":405},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":406},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":407},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_891_1#1$1","duration":"1","isblock":"true","id":408},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"娜斯提","text":"......","id":409,"figure":"avg_npc_891_1#1$1"},{"type":"dialog","id":410},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"1","id":411},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_892_1#1$1","duration":"1.5","id":412},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":413},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_892_1#9$1","focus":"l","id":414},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"小贾斯汀","text":"娜斯提，你没有选个视野更好的地方吗？","id":415,"figure":"avg_npc_892_1#9$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_891_1#6$1","focus":"r","id":416},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"娜斯提","text":"......你什么时候才能不继续烦我？","id":417,"figure":"avg_npc_891_1#6$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_892_1#9$1","focus":"l","id":418},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"小贾斯汀","text":"我去莱塔尼亚考察的时候，曾看过莱塔尼亚人的烟花庆典，他们会邀请最好的作曲家，专门为这场庆典谱曲。","id":419,"figure":"avg_npc_892_1#9$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_892_1#3$1","focus":"l","id":420},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"小贾斯汀","text":"当第一朵烟花绽放，音乐家们就会一齐演奏，那场面，啧啧，真是漂亮。","id":421,"figure":"avg_npc_892_1#3$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_891_1#6$1","focus":"r","id":422},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"娜斯提","text":"你的修辞过于贫乏，莱塔尼亚人不会喜欢你。","id":423,"figure":"avg_npc_891_1#6$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_892_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":424},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"小贾斯汀","text":"是啊，不过，我们今天居然在特里蒙看到了同样灿烂的景色。","id":425,"figure":"avg_npc_892_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"小贾斯汀","text":"悬浮在天顶的圆环，无人机的子弹曳出的光雨，装甲上溅射出的火花......","id":426,"figure":"avg_npc_892_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"小贾斯汀","text":"不比烟花庆典差。","id":427,"figure":"avg_npc_892_1#1$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_892_1#9$1","focus":"l","id":428},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"小贾斯汀","text":"算算时间，演奏该进入高潮部分了吧。","id":429,"figure":"avg_npc_892_1#9$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"小贾斯汀","text":"应该有一个震撼人心的强音——","id":430,"figure":"avg_npc_892_1#9$1"},{"type":"dialog","id":431},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":432},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":433},{"type":"background","id":434},{"type":"charslot","id":435},{"type":"Image","image":"38_i10","xScale":"1.8","yScale":"1.8","x":"50","y":"200","screenadapt":"coverall","id":436},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":437},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":438},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"-1","xstrength":"2","ystrength":"10","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":439},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_avg_energybeamfire","volume":"0.6","id":440},{"type":"Image","image":"38_i16","screenadapt":"coverall","xScale":"1.8","yScale":"1.8","x":"50","y":"200","fadetime":"0.2","id":441},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":442},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0.05","block":"true","id":443},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0.05","block":"true","id":444},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0.05","block":"true","id":445},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"1","block":"false","id":446},{"type":"ImageTween","xTo":"50","yTo":"-180","duration":"3.5","id":447},{"type":"delay","time":"3","id":448},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_avg_beamamb","volume":"1","id":449},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":450},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"1.5","xstrength":"4","ystrength":"30","vibrato":"50","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":451},{"type":"ImageTween","xScaleFrom":"1.8","yScaleFrom":"1.8","xScaleTo":"1.2","yScaleTo":"1.2","duration":"0.2","ease":"InOutCubic","xTo":"0","yTo":"0","block":"true","id":452},{"type":"Image","image":"38_i16","screenadapt":"coverall","xScale":"2.5","yScale":"2.5","fadetime":"0.1","id":453},{"type":"ImageTween","xScaleFrom":"2.5","yScaleFrom":"2.5","xScaleTo":"1.2","yScaleTo":"1.2","duration":"0.1","ease":"InOutCubic","xTo":"0","yTo":"0","block":"true","id":454},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":455},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"6","xstrength":"30","ystrength":"30","vibrato":"50","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":456},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$glass","volume":"1","id":457},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_avg_collapse","volume":"1","id":458},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_gen_thunders_amb","volume":"0.7","id":459},{"type":"ImageTween","xScaleFrom":"1.2","yScaleFrom":"1.2","xScaleTo":"1","yScaleTo":"1","duration":"20","id":460},{"type":"delay","time":"3.5","id":461},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"小贾斯汀","text":"......","id":462},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"娜斯提","text":"......","id":463},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"小贾斯汀","text":"这......比我想象的还漂亮，莱茵生命该向城市里所有欣赏到这一幕的人收费。","id":464},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"娜斯提","text":"......成功了，聚焦发生器的材料和结构暂时抵抗住了能量束的冲击。","id":465},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"娜斯提","text":"接下来是充能和聚焦阶段，只要能收集到这种高压条件下的读数......","id":466},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"小贾斯汀","text":"接下来，军方和梅兰德的人恐怕会抓住最后的机会，阻止聚焦的完成。","id":467},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"小贾斯汀","text":"你就不担心总辖？","id":468},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"娜斯提","text":"她什么时候需要我们担心。","id":469},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"娜斯提","text":"我们是同行者，我们只是同行者。","id":470},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"娜斯提","text":"我们只需要做好自己的事，然后......祝她好运。","id":471},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"娜斯提","text":"（萨卡兹语）若有一天，卡兹戴尔亦悬于天顶，我将在火炉上镌刻你的名字。","id":472},{"type":"dialog","id":473},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":474},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":475},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":476},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":477},{"type":"charslot","id":478},{"type":"Image","id":479}],"characters":["？？？","凯尔希","赫默","雅拉","“保存者”","娜斯提","小贾斯汀"]}